                        Prosciutto Crostini with Burrata

   Sarah

   3 years ago

   Prosciutto Crostini: These quick crostini feature crispy prosciutto,
   creamy burrata, and a simple lemon honey drizzle sauce.
   Prosciutto Crostini: These quick crostini feature crispy prosciutto,
   creamy burrata, and a simple lemon honey drizzle sauce.

   Is there anything so amazing as the perfect little hors d‚Äôoeuvre that
   is the crostini? I am a bruschetta and crostini fiend, and so these
   prosciutto crostini with burrata and lemon honey drizzle really hit the
   spot!

   Prosciutto Crostini: These quick crostini feature crispy prosciutto,
   creamy burrata, and a simple lemon honey drizzle sauce. Prosciutto
   Crostini: These quick crostini feature crispy prosciutto, creamy
   burrata, and a simple lemon honey drizzle sauce.

